			<div class="content" id="post-content-794344">
									

<p>I'm a bit of an obsessive-compulsive type, so I started checking out your calculations for times.</p>
<p>60 seconds on power level 3 = 60x60x60 seconds = 216&nbsp;000 seconds x (1 hour/3600 seconds) x (24 hours/day) = 2.5 days</p>
<p>Maybe the coffee on power level 3 test would be noticed as separated or something? Or upshift the power to level 4:</p>
<p>60 seconds on power level 4 = 60^4 seconds = 12&nbsp;960&nbsp;000 seconds x (1 hour/3600 seconds) x (24 hours/day) = 150 days, or about 5 months</p>
<p>For the two months tests—<br />
47 seconds on power level 4 = 47^4 seconds = 4&nbsp;879&nbsp;681 seconds x (1 hour/3600 seconds) x (24 hours/day) = about 56 days, or about 2 months</p>
<p>Otherwise, awesome!! Well-thought tests!</p>

							</div>

								
