														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2360383">
									

<p>Also, while we're nitpicking about aging of alcoholic beverages - this thing wouldn't work all that well for wine, either.</p>
<p>The taste of wine is influenced by the weather of the year it was harvested - which wouldn't be changed by SCP-119. So, if your wine is from a bad year, it would *still* be a bad year.</p>

							</div>

								
					
