			<div class="content" id="post-content-3810405">
									

<p>I think the first two tests with the coffee cup are my favorite. Not to say the other tests are bad or uninteresting, but this is what went through my head:<br />
&quot;Ugh, gotta reheat my morning coffee. Guess I'll use the new microwave we got. What the hell? It's not even warm! If it didn't warm at all, lets try&#8230; power level 4. Oh what the fuck&#8230;&quot;</p>

